	Add new test functions
	* include/abg-fwd.h (is_function_decl, is_decl, is_namespace)
	(is_scope_decl): Declare new function overloads.
	* src/abg-ir.cc (is_function_decl, is_decl, is_namespace)
	(is_scope_decl): Define them.

