2015-07-15  Dodji Seketeli <dodji@redhat.com>

	Various style fixes
	* abipkgdiff.cc (get_soname_of_elf_file): Fix spacing.
	* tools/abipkgdiff.cc (elf_file_paths): Make this global variable
	static.
