	* tests/data/test-diff-suppr/test6-fn-suppr-report-4.txt: New test input.
	* tests/data/test-diff-suppr/test6-fn-suppr-v0.cc: Source code for
	new test input.
	* tests/data/test-diff-suppr/test6-fn-suppr-v1.cc: Source code for
	new test input.
